'''冰島國教會'''（{{lang-is|Þjóðkirkjan}}），又稱'''冰島福音信義會'''（{{lang-is|Hin evangelíska lúterska kirkja}}），是[[冰島|冰島]]的[[國教會|國教會]]，信仰屬於[[信義宗|信義宗]]，並且是[[鮑渥共融|鮑渥共融]]的成員。冰島國教會現任的主教是Agnes M. Sigurðardóttir，她是首位擔任冰島福音信義會主教的女性<ref>{{cite web|title=Agnes M Sigurdardóttir is first woman elected as bishop in Icelan|url=http://www.zonta.org/MemberResources/Messages/MessageView/tabid/194/ArticleId/167/Agnes-M-Sigurdardottir-is-first-woman-elected-as-bishop-in-Iceland.aspx|publisher=Zonta International|accessdate=11 January 2013|date=15 May 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610220135/http://www.zonta.org/MemberResources/Messages/MessageView/tabid/194/ArticleId/167/Agnes-M-Sigurdardottir-is-first-woman-elected-as-bishop-in-Iceland.aspx|archive-date=2015-06-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

